    • coordinateInsert

      public GeneratedValues coordinateInsert(Object id, Object[] values, Object entity, SharedSessionContractImplementor session)
      Perform the insert(s).
      Parameters:
      id - This is the id as known in memory. For post-insert id generation (IDENTITY, etc) this will be null.
      values - The extracted attribute values
      entity - The entity instance being persisted
      session - The originating context
      Returns:
      The generated values if any, null otherwise.
